        "text_rByTwT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You are invited to join one of our exclusive <strong>Atelier Modernista Jewellery Subscriptions</strong> completely individualised to you. Offering <strong>6–18 pieces of handmade Bauhaus-inspired jewellery</strong> over the year, advance access to new designers before they launch on the store, and discounts across Atelier Modernista’s shop, our exclusive subscriptions specialise in taking jewellery very personally.</p><p>Plus exclusive invitations, early sale access, and surprise treats. <em>Starts at £15/month.</em></p><p><strong>The MODERNISTA Subscription: £15 per month for 12 months</strong></p><p>• One piece of Atelier Modernista jewellery tailored to your tastes, delivered every 8 weeks for a year (6 jewellery deliveries per annum)<br/>• Early access to new designers before they launch on the store</p><p><strong>The CALLIGRAPHER Subscription: £25 per month for 12 months</strong></p><p>• Two pieces of Atelier Modernista jewellery tailored to your tastes, delivered every 8 weeks for a year (6 deliveries per annum)<br/>• One design-led surprise gift in every delivery.<br/>• 10% off the Atelier Modernista store.<br/>• Early access to new designers before they launch on the store.<br/>• Members-only access to limited runs.</p><p><strong>The ICON Subscription: £40 per month for 12 months</strong></p><p>• Three pieces of Atelier Modernista jewellery tailored to your tastes, delivered every 8 weeks for a year (6 deliveries per annum)<br/>• One design-led surprise gift in every delivery.<br/>• 20% off the Atelier Modernista store.<br/>• Early access to new designers before they launch on the store.<br/>• Members-only access to limited runs.<br/>• Priority access to Archive Editions.<br/>• Early Sale Access</p>",
